Don't cause trouble and I won't
have to hurt you.
Well, I'd better be off.
Come home soon,okay?
Go and report it to the captain.
Understood.
Ugh, another rough day...
Tell me about it... Maybe over a drink?
Me hungry like Volff...
Welcome home!
Feels good to be back!
I know a really nice place.
Wanna go together?
Okay! Same place tomorrow!

Don't you need to attend
to the shop out front?

I haven't been feeling so great lately,
so my son's been handling it for me...
Oh, bother, bother!
Urk...

How about going to a hospital instead
of hanging round here? Just a thought...
Are you going to war too, Daddy?
Do you have to?

Dadapooon!
Mamapoooon!
Where you go?
Now that's a big castle...

There's nothing like that in Gula,
that's for sure.
Where the littlepons gone off to?
Just focus on the job, all right?
We gotta fix this up before nightfall.

Wouldn't want anyone falling
and having an accident.

My friend's gone to Gula.
I wonder if they're doing fine...
Mama, can I buy a sweetie?

Oh, all right then.
But just the one!
I feel sorry for the soldiers...
What's up with that guy?

He just drank too much.
Same old story!

Sometimes I crave an open-air bath...
It's not weird, is it?

Air here taste more spicier
than me thought!
Where did I put it...? Hmm...

You'd better find that key.
I'm not sleeping outside!

This open-air hot spring is the best in
the empire.
I could happily come here every day!

That big Divine Beast weapon's
gone now, huh.
Maybe it went back to the palace?

Quick, quick!
Somebody maybe come!

Shut up!
Just be patient.
Where do you want to go today?
I think I'd like to look at board games!
You got anything new?

Yessir! Got a new shipment in just 
yesterday.
Taste all right to you?
Yeff! It'f delifiouf!

Have you any tactical
manuals in stock?
Allow me to take a look...

When I'm all grown up,
I wanna be a salvager!
Me want be soldier!
Over here this time, huh...?
Let's just get it over with quickly.
Hm, what should I make today...
These veggies here are very popular.

Granny, 
come on, come on, come on!

I'm coming,
I'm coming.

Wow! Whoa!
Superbia is AWESOME.

I can't believe how
bright it is at night!
Come on, Boss! Leave some for me too!
Nuh-uh! It's all mine!
You can't just do that!

Bwaah!
I'm sorry...
You've got that faraway look again.

Oh, just remembering my
days with the army band...

Even the requests on the notice board
sound kind of violent lately...
They're so lucky...
The security here's impressive!

Is very important place,
what friend expect?
Shit... I drank too much...

You'd better consider your
limits next time...

Today we'll be patrolling around
the laboratories!
Sir! Yes! Sir!

So many bathhouses!
Which one do I go to today?
It too briiight!
Are we sure it not explode?
Plenty of stuff to transport today, huh?
Yeah, it's gonna be another tough day...
Ugh... I'm totally lost.
Late on first day of job?! Unbelievable.
This door is not door that open?
Yeah, you don't see it open very often...
Here, let me help.
Thank you!
What kind of place is Avaritia?

Is very busy! Lots of busyness!
Friend should visit and help economy!
Still working at this hour?
Hey, quality work takes time.
How are you doing over there?
Nearly done!

Just what you'd expect
from a military facility.

Let's head back before
people show up.

What the heck is this graffiti...?
Some kind of new code?
Wanna go shopping together?
I guess so...
Ooh, aren't you a strapping fellow!

Why don't you come have
a bite to eat at my place?

Hey, I'm sorry.
I tried my best, but...

The older kids get to play
out in the open. Not fair!

Hey, that's dangerous!
Come back at once!

Look, Dad! There's some sort
of entrance down below!

I've been seeing lots of Drivers
around the palace recently.

I've heard they've been
recruiting far and wide.

I can't hear you, maggots!
Answer me like you mean it!

Sir!
Yes! Sir!

Sir!
Yes! Sir!

Sir!
Yes! Sir!

Sir!
Yes! Sir!

Tomorrow's training is harder
than today's! Aren't you all glad?!

Sir!
Yes!!! Sir!!!

Sir!
Yes!!! Sir!!!

Sir!
Yes!!! Sir!!!

Sir!
Yes!!! Sir!!!

Sir!
Yes!!! Sir!!!
Ugh, I give up...
One! Two! Three!

Whoever fails this exercise gets
a one-way ticket to Gula!
How many ships was it today...?
I hear they're developing a new model.
Does it look fixable?
This part keeps breaking, doesn't it...

Now I hear we've got
internal enemies, too?
No rest for the wicked, say I.

You better be ready for battle.
Make sure you know how to use this.
I will.
Let's play ball!

Yeah!
And after that, we can play soldiers!

What do I do...? I think I dropped that
key somewhere around here...

Losing the key to the harbor gates...
My CO is gonna be so pissed!

I can't find it anywhere... Don't tell me
it's fallen right off the bridge...!

Fabelle's never gonna let me hear
the end of this... I'll just have to
keep searching tomorrow.
That's a big vehicle!

The Divine Beast battleships that came to
Gula were bigger still, y'know...
Me bring cargo to town on double!
This crate too heavy, meh...
Nice load of cargo you've got there.

Everything is above board!
Me check twice myself!!
Much brighter than torches, isn't it?
The city's brighter still, you'll see.
Why it so dusty?!

Dust get in mouth!
Pftheh! Pthooie!

Please use the far lift
for transporting Armus.
Why, is this one off-limits?

Pay attention when you're
operating this thing.

Are you sure you've
stacked everything?
Mind you don't offend anyone.
It's not my first guard shift you know...

Doing maintenance on this geothermal
plant is pretty dangerous work.

I've asked them loads of times, but the
army can't fix the monster problem...

We use the gondola to get around here.
There's a lot of monsters on dry land...

So...hot... It's like Superbia's Divine Beast
is running a fever!

If you fall in there, you'll... Let's just
say you don't want to fall in there.

I'm actually afraid of heights? I don't
know why they put me up here...
Let's just keep each other secure,okay?

The industrial lift's on the left.
Lift for people's a bit further in.

Can we hurry and go
to Alba Margen now?
Let's we go!

Huh... Got in through
that little gap, huh?
Don't fall out of the elevator.
I wanna go hoooome!

...There are procedures for
that sort of thing.
Where's everyone gone...?
Aren't you hungry?
...I'll be fine... Ugh...
